STATE EX. REL. FREED
v.
DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL 2018-0609 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 1, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's motion to refer counsel and motion to accept amended affidavit denied as moot.
